{"code":200,"message":"OK","tweet":{"url":"https://x.com/WesRoth/status/2026492362445185186","id":"2026492362445185186","text":"Notion has launched Custom Agents introducing fully autonomous AI teammates that run continuously in the background to handle recurring, multi-step workflows.\n\nUnlike previous \"Ask AI\" features that required manual prompting, Custom Agents operate entirely on their own. Users set a trigger (like a new database entry) or a schedule (like every Friday at 4 PM), and the agent handles the execution 24/7.","raw_text":{"text":"Notion has launched Custom Agents introducing fully autonomous AI teammates that run continuously in the background to handle recurring, multi-step workflows.\n\nUnlike previous \"Ask AI\" features that required manual prompting, Custom Agents operate entirely on their own. Users set a trigger (like a new database entry) or a schedule (like every Friday at 4 PM), and the agent handles the execution 24/7.","display_text_range":[0,403],"facets":[{"type":"media","indices":[281,304],"id":"2026447888801476610","display":"pic.x.com/hXDRsrlKPT","original":"https://t.co/hXDRsrlKPT","replacement":"https://x.com/WesRoth/status/2026492362445185186/video/1"}]},"author":{"screen_name":"WesRoth","url":"https://x.com/WesRoth","id":"1547403906954563585","followers":35967,"following":831,"likes":22246,"media_count":8248,"name":"Wes Roth","description":"FOLLOWS YOU.    Artificial Intelligence, Automation & Optimism. Everything I say is 100% serious...","raw_description":{"text":"FOLLOWS YOU.    Artificial Intelligence, Automation & Optimism. Everything I say is 100% serious...","facets":[]},"location":"San Diego, CA","banner_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1547403906954563585/1758421858","avatar_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1905477529013813251/RST2MxqV_200x200.jpg","joined":"Thu Jul 14 02:13:59 +0000 2022","protected":false,"website":{"url":"https://youtube.com/@wesroth","display_url":"youtube.com/@wesroth"},"ve